  "title": "Project Engineer [HDB Project]",
  "description": "<p>Job Description &amp; Requirements</p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>To conduct and carry out TBM and allocate the task to supervisors and team.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and submit Daily, Weekly and Monthly construction report.</li>\n  <li>To monitor the site progress and highlight obstructions to carry out works.</li>\n  <li>Ensure site team perform all the activities in safe and effective manner.</li>\n  <li>Assist in technical studies and prepare for monthly progress claim.</li>\n  <li>Assist in project schedule by studying project plan and specifications, plan schedule and sequencing project elements.</li>\n  <li>Maintain project schedule by monitoring project progress, coordinating activities, and resolving problems.</li>\n  <li>Prepares project progress reports by collecting, analysing, and summarizing information and trends.</li>\n  <li>Maintains safe and clean working environment by enforcing procedures, rules, and regulations.</li>\n  <li>Maintains project data base, entering and backing up data.</li>\n  <li>Prepare the site progress photos for progress.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Educational Qualification: Diploma in Engineering (Civil/Mechanical) or equivalent.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years experience in Residential Construction industry.</li>\n</ul>",
